16:["$","p","13",{"className":"text-[#B3B3B3] leading-relaxed my-3","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"If you're a DJ who carries 7-inch records to gigs, you need storage that survives transport. Cardboard deteriorates. Plastic crates designed for 12-inch records are oversized and wasteful. This box is sized exactly for 7-inch singles — records stay upright, stay in order, and don't shift during transport."}}]
17:["$","p","14",{"className":"text-[#B3B3B3] leading-relaxed my-3","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"If you're a collector, the customization options mean your storage can reflect your collection. A box with your label name on it stops being furniture and starts being part of the listening room aesthetic."}}]
