1c:["$","p","19",{"className":"text-[#B3B3B3] leading-relaxed my-3","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"It's practical, it's handmade, it's personalized, and it's from a maker who actually plays records. That combination is rare at any price point, and at $75 it's genuinely exceptional value for a made-to-order, customized piece."}}]
